search_results.title: About — Janet Fitch
search_results.snippet: Janet Fitch is an American author and teacher of fiction writing. She is the author of the #1 national bestseller White Oleander.

search_results.title: Biography | Janet Horvath, Cellist, Writer, Speaker
search_results.snippet: Janet Horvath, the Minnesota Orchestra's associate principal cello from 1980 to 2012, is a lifelong performing classical musician, soloist, author, and speaker.

search_results.title: Janet S Fox, Author and Big Picture Story Coach
search_results.snippet: I'm Janet! I'm the author of 13 books for young readers, 7 from major publishers, with a 25-year career in writing and publishing.
